Global Food Safety Big Data Market Insights
Food Safety Big Data Market size was valued at USD 15.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 25.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Food Safety Big Data Market Overview
The global Food Safety Big Data market is projected to reach a market value of USD 19.5 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.5% from 2023 to 2030. This market growth is driven by the increasing need for traceability, transparency, and safety within the food industry. Key market players are leveraging big data analytics to monitor food safety in real-time, helping to reduce risks of contamination and improve quality control. Technological advancements in data processing, AI, and machine learning further enhance the potential of big data in the food safety sector.

